text: Andriy Fedechko (born 4 December 1990) is a Ukrainian modern pentathlete. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's event. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male modern pentathletes Category:Olympic modern pentathletes of Ukraine Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:World Modern Pentathlon Championships medalists
